import axios from "axios"; import React from "react"; import { useState } from "react"; function Signup() { const [form, setForm] = useState({ form, name: "", email: "", password: "", mobile: "", gender: "", country: "", status: "Unblock" }); const onchange = (e) => { setForm({ ...form, id: new Date().getTime().toString(), [e.target.name]: e.target.value, }); }; const submit = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); const res = await axios.post("http://localhost:3000/user").then(() => { setForm({ form, name: "", email: "", password: "", mobile: "", gender: "", country: "", status: "Unblock" }); }); }; return (
); } export default Signup;
